data.description: Major price reduction - Seller wants an offer! Come see this lovely home on gorgeous acreage between Rockford & Freeman nestled under Mica Peak! Nearly 12 acres featuring a seasonal creek, pasture potential for large animals, established fruit trees, and tons of garden space. Watch deer, elk, moose, turkeys and quail from the deck! Plenty of space in the over 2700 sq ft,  5 Bed, 2 Bath house. Huge kitchen with tons of storage and pantry closet. Scenery out every window. A large family room in the walk-out basement is the perfect place for a rec-room, game room or whatever you need a large space for. Fifth bedroom is well-suited to be an in-home office. New siding and metal roof means no maintenance for years to come. Peaceful beauty in every season of the year. One-of-a-kind and need to see to appreciate! Possible Seller Assistance with an acceptable offer. Buyers using a preferred lender at Guardian Mortgage may qualify for up to 1% Lender Credit!
